reviewText: This is old-school nude dancing (not so much stripping as we know it today--not as much exposure, no monolithic pole and not a whole lot of actual disrobing). Most of the girls are natural (good) but not especially attractive (bad). It's REALLY hard to tell one from another. They're also entirely anonymous, which makes me wonder what they're doing today and if their children (or grandchildren) know that they were in this production. Also something about this feels very European; hard to say for sure because it has basically zero details and it's clearly from a videotape master. So don't expect much in the way of image quality.
